data.description: Nestled in the sought-after Sundance, this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath residence sits gracefully on a peaceful cul-de-sac! The great room welcomes you with its wood-look flooring, abundant natural light, and backyard access, setting a warm and inviting tone. The kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting granite counters, shaker cabinets with crown moulding, a chic mosaic tile backsplash, SS appliances, pendant and recessed lighting, a pantry, and a peninsula with a breakfast bar. You'll also find a versatile den and a loft, ideal for entertainment or relaxation. The main bedroom is a personal sanctuary adorned with plush carpeting and an ensuite with dual sinks. Discover a backyard oasis with a covered patio and shimmering pool, perfect for sunny relaxation or hosting gatherings. Make this gem yours!
